{"serial": "85013", "department_serial": 70, "code": "BM2043", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Microelectronics", "ch": "微電子學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "醫學工程與資訊科學組"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Chen-Han"], "ch": ["黃貞翰"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "R3", "room": "106"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "生醫科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Biomedical Sciences and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 3, "selected": 31, "remark": {"ch": "醫學工程與資訊科學組", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "-了解基本的微電子學、電子電路設計與分析。\n-設計基於直流分析和小信號模型的放大器電路並提升實作能力。\n-使用集總電路模型和運算放大器設計電子電路並提升實作能力。\n-經由電子設計與分析方法，熟悉應用微電子學的基礎內容。\n-培養發展獨立思考與跨領域創新能力。", "en": "-To understand the basic analyses of electronic circuit. \n-To design amplifiers circuit based on dc analysis and small signal model. \n-To familiarize the concept of Biomedical Electronics by designing electronic circuits using lumped circuit models and OP amps."}, "outline": {"ch": "第01週\n回顧電晶體與場效電晶體原理與應用\n第02週\n理想運算放大器\n第03週\n非理想運算放大器\n第04週\n運算放大器的小信號運算(I)\n第05週\n運算放大器的小信號運算(II)\n第06週\n其他無源效應和放大器設計\n第07週\n頻率響應分析\n第08週\n考試(I)\n第09週\n積分器與微分器(I)\n第10週\n積分器與微分器(II)\n第11週\n濾波器設計(I)\n第12週\n濾波器設計(II)\n第13週\n儀表放大器\n第14週\n比較器與史密特觸發器\n第15週\n積體電路型偏置電流源，電流鏡和電流轉向電路\n第16週\n實驗(I)基本運算電路設計應用\n第17週\n實驗(II)濾波器設計應用\n第18週\n考試(II)", "en": "Week 1\nReview of MOSFETs, BJTs and amplifiers\nWeek 2\nIdeal operational amplifiers with inverting and non-Inverting configuration\nWeek 3\nNon-ideal operational amplifiers with inverting and non-Inverting configuration\nWeek 4\nSmall signal operation of operational amplifiers (I)\nWeek 5\nSmall signal operation of operational amplifiers (II)\nWeek 6\nOther non-ideal effects and amplifier design with active load\nWeek 7\nFrequency response analysis\nWeek 8\nExam (I)\nWeek 9\nintegrator and differentiator (I)\nWeek 10\nintegrator and differentiator (II)\nWeek 11\nFilter Design (I)\nWeek 12\nFilter Design (II)\nWeek 13\nInstrumentation amplifier\nWeek 14\nComparator and Schmitt trigger\nWeek 15\nIC bias current source, current mirror and current steering circuit\nWeek 16\nExperiment (I) Basic operation circuit design and application\nWeek 17\nExperiment (II) Filter design and application\nWeek 18\nExam (II)"}, "textbook": {"ch": "- 自製講義\n參考書:\n- 微電子電路分析與設計: Donald Neamen.\n- 電子電路於生物醫學儀器的分析與應用: Robert B. Northrop.", "en": "- Lecture notes\nsuggested reading materials:\n- Microelectronics Circuit Analysis and Design: Donald Neamen.\n- Analysis and Application of Analog Electronic Circuits to Biomedical Instrumentation: Robert B. Northrop."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席10%\n作業30%\n期中考30%\n期末考30%", "en": "Participation  10%\nAssignments  30%\nMidterm Exam  30%\nTerm Exam  30%"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "(四)10:00-13:00", "en": "(THU)10:00-13:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "生醫生化技術領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n醫學電子資訊與影像處理", "en": "生醫生化技術領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n醫學電子資訊與影像處理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "學習數物化、醫學、生物等科學基礎與精進知識、思辨邏輯及運用能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "執行實驗設計、數據分析與推論的能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉臨床醫學，並培養生醫器材或材料之設計、開發、及場域應用的能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉感測元件原理、訓練製造、設計與整合智慧系統", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "發掘、探究、解析、處理以及重構問題", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "培養多層面跨域整合與團隊合作", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "瞭解專業知識與人本倫理間的調和、以及技術對環境、社會之影響，並能持續學習", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙